{"tid":972071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"釋昭慧挺蔡英文　「我不用穿著袈裟踢正步了」","createTime":"2019-01-07T06:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T06:47:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abd3ab5275b198eb81d2cc6049593b9b82f39c90","tid":972071,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190105/1495236/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190105%2F1495236%2F&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=77fc177c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190105%2F1495236%2F&h=d4088e27\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190105/1495236/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/776/d776879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F776%2Fd776879.jpg&h=3d15062f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統強勢回擊中國的「一國兩制」迎好評，法師釋昭慧也讚聲！<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平周三(2日)在《告台灣同胞書》40周年紀念會上，推崇「一國兩制」是實現統一台灣的最佳方式，更自認「中國夢是兩岸同胞共同的夢」。但總統蔡英文馬上戳破這個「中國夢」，直言「台灣絕大多數的民意，都不會接受一國兩制」，反對一國兩制是「台灣共識」，迎來台灣網友許多正面肯定。<br />\n<br />\n法師釋昭慧也在臉書說，「只要蔡總統在位，我就不用穿著袈裟踢正步，舉著國旗進廣場。」還特別說明「無論舉的是哪國國旗，這種滑稽動作，都會讓我失去僧格！」，顯然對蔡英文回嗆中國的表現頗為讚賞。"},{"pid":"3d9f5031fb1e405ff007bb50a01b4e5264710cc7","tid":972071,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41afe29f69e2da38b9963b95abaaa9fa99f74df","tid":972071,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"人地又係釋，香港個幾隻又係釋，點解差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通隔住個海真係好過隔住條河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307e72d19c41097a82a5325a3c4f5d7b1fed67e6","tid":972071,"uid":61271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e41afe29f69e2da38b9963b95abaaa9fa99f74df","tid":972071,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"人地又係釋，香港個幾隻又係釋，點解差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通隔住個海真係好過隔住條河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"人地個女總統對抗大陸<br />\n香港個女特首係習近平隻狗<br />\n<br />\n點同？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}